                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "74fd4b78b1a679acb12014cc5bd3ccf6",
                "text": "An effect with the death trait kills you immediately if it reduces you to 0 HP. Some death effects can bring you closer to death or slay you outright without reducing you to 0 HP."
            },
            {
